+  # Mini Ultra Plan 2 / Phase L2 — opt-in runner-scoped local routing.
+  # Active ONLY when a run is started with --runtime-profile local_qwen
+  # AND the runner name appears in allowed_runners. Every other runner
+  # and every run on a different profile is unaffected (default cloud
+  # cascade). When activated:
+  #   * llm_call events carry provider="local", model="local/<host>/<model>"
+  #   * source="runner:<name>" via the per-runner InferenceAuthority sibling
+  #   * fallback is "none" — a runner-scope local failure must surface,
